points.title: Your personal data may be used for marketing purposes

points.title: Information is provided about what kind of information they collect
points.status: Privacy policy: "Types of Data Collected". In a large font, includes the following sub-titles: "Personal Data" and "Usage Data".

points.title: The terms for this service are easy to read
points.status: In the privacy policy, the font is big, there is lots of sections and further division, important terms are bolded, and there is good text spacing (sometimes even double lined).

points.title: Information is provided about how your personal data is used
points.status: In the privacy policy, there is a large section titled, "Use of Your Personal Data".

points.title: Your IP address is collected, which can be used to view your approximate location
points.status: Privacy policy: "Usage Data may include information such as Your Device's Internet Protocol address (e.g. IP address) [...]"

points.title: Blocking first party cookies may limit your ability to use the service
points.status: Privacy policy: "However, if You do not accept Cookies, You may not be able to use some parts of our Service"

points.title: Do Not Track (DNT) headers are ignored and you are tracked anyway even if you set this header.
points.status: Privacy policy: "Our Service does not respond to Do Not Track signals"

points.title: This service gives your personal data to third parties involved in its operation
points.status: Privacy policy: "We may share Your personal information in the following situations: [...] With Service Providers: We may share Your personal information with Service Providers to monitor and analyze the use of our Service, for payment processing, to contact You"

points.title: Your personal data may be sold or otherwise transferred as part of a bankruptcy proceeding or other type of financial transaction
points.status: Privacy policy: "The company may use Personal Data for the following purposes: [...] For business transfers: We may use Your information to evaluate or conduct a merger, divestiture, restructuring, reorganization, dissolution, or other sale or transfer of some or all of Our assets, whether as a going concern or as part of bankruptcy, liquidation, or similar proceeding, in which Personal Data held by Us about our Service users is among the assets transferred"

points.title: You are tracked via web beacons, tracking pixels, browser fingerprinting, and/or device fingerprinting
points.status: Privacy policy: "Tracking technologies used are beacons, tags, and scripts to collect and track information and to improve and analyze Our Service"

points.title: Information is provided about how they collect personal data
points.status: In the privacy policy, there is a large section titled, "Tracking Technologies and Cookies".

points.title: First-party cookies are used
points.status: Privacy policy: "We use Cookies and similar tracking technologies to track the activity on Our Service and store certain information"

points.title: You can opt out of promotional communications
points.status: Privacy policy: "You may opt-out of receiving any, or all, of these communications from Us by following the unsubscribe link or instructions provided in any email We send or by contacting Us"

points.title: Some personal data may be kept for business interests or legal obligations
points.status: Privacy policy: "We will retain and use Your Personal Data to the extent necessary to comply with our legal obligations (for example, if we are required to retain your data to comply with applicable laws), resolve disputes, and enforce our legal agreements and policies"

points.title: Web beacons are used in service-to-user communication
points.status: Privacy policy: "Certain sections of our Service and our emails may contain small electronic files known as web beacons (also referred to as clear gifs, pixel tags, and single-pixel gifs) that permit the Company, for example, to count users who have visited those pages or opened an email"

points.title: Third-party cookies are used for statistics
points.status: Privacy policy: "We may use third-party Service providers to monitor and analyze the use of our Service."

points.title: You can request access, correction and/or deletion of your data
points.status: Privacy policy: "You have the right to request the deletion of Your Personal Data, subject to certain exceptions. Once We receive and confirm Your request, We will delete (and direct Our Service Providers to delete) Your personal information from our records, unless an exception applies"

points.title: The service claims to be CCPA compliant for California users
points.status: Privacy policy: "This privacy notice section for California residents supplements the information contained in Our Privacy Policy and it applies solely to all visitors, users, and others who reside in the State of California"

points.title: The service claims to be GDPR compliant for European users
points.status: In the privacy policy, under a section titled, "Your Rights under the GDPR", it states, The Company undertakes to respect the confidentiality of Your Personal Data and to guarantee You can exercise Your rights"

points.title: You can opt out of targeted advertising
points.status: Privacy policy: "You can opt out of receiving ads that are personalized as served by our Service Providers by following our instructions presented on the Service"

points.title: A free help desk is provided

points.title: The service is provided 'as is' and to be used at your sole risk
points.status: Terms of Use: "The Service is provided to You 'AS IS' and 'AS AVAILABLE' and with all faults and defects without warranty of any kind"

points.title: When the service wants to make a material change to its terms, you are notified at least 30 days in advance
points.status: Terms of Use: "We reserve the right, at Our sole discretion, to modify or replace these Terms at any time. If a revision is material We will make reasonable efforts to provide at least 30 days' notice prior to any new terms taking effect. What constitutes a material change will be determined at Our sole discretion"

points.title: You are being tracked via social media cookies/pixels
points.status: Privacy policy: "We use the Facebook Insights function in connection with the operation of the Facebook Fan Page and on the basis of the GDPR, in order to obtain anonymized statistical data about Our users"

points.title: Your personal information is used for many different purposes
points.status: In the privacy policy, under the section about the usage of personal data: "To provide and maintain our Service [...] To manage Your Account [...] For the performance of a contact [...] To contact You [...] To provide You with [...] information [...] To manage Your requests [...] For business transfers [...] For other purposes: We may use Your information for other purposes, such as data analysis, identifying usage trends, determining the effectiveness of our promotional campaigns and to evaluate and improve our Service, products, services, marketing and your experience"

points.title: This service receives your precise location through GPS coordinates
points.status: Privacy policy: "While using Our Service, We may ask You to provide Us with certain personally identifiable information that can be used to contact or identify You. Personally identifiable information may include, but is not limited to: [...] Address, State, Province, ZIP/Postal code, City"

points.title: Your Personal data may be sold unless you opt out
points.status: Privacy Policy: "The Service Providers we partner with (for example, our analytics or advertising partners) may use technology on the Service that sells personal information as defined by the CCPA law. If you wish to opt out of the use of Your personal information for interest-based advertising purposes and these potential sales as defined under CCPA law, you may do so by following the instructions below."

points.title: You are prohibited from sending chain letters, junk mail, spam or any unsolicited messages
points.status: Terms of Use: "Examples of such objectionable Content include [...] Spam, machine – or randomly – generated, constituting unauthorized or unsolicited advertising, chain letters, any other form of unauthorized solicitation, or any form of lottery or gambling"

points.title: You cannot delete your account of this service
points.status: Terms of Use: "Upon termination, Your right to use the Service will cease immediately. If You wish to terminate Your Account, You may simply discontinue using the Service". The wording makes it seem like if you do not want an account anymore, the only thing you can do is to not use the service, and that accounts can only be deleted by the company, not the users themselves.

points.title: You maintain ownership of your content
points.status: Terms of Use: "You retain any and all of Your rights to any Content You submit, post or display on or through the Service and You are responsible for protecting those rights"

points.title: You agree not to submit libelous, harassing or threatening content
points.status: Terms of Use: "You may not transmit any Content that is [...] threatening, libelous, defamatory, [...]"

points.title: You agree not to use the service for illegal purposes

points.title: You are prohibited from posting content which promotes violence or politically or religiously extremist values.

points.title: If you offer suggestions to the service, they become the owner of the ideas that you give them

points.title: You agree to comply with the law of the service's country

points.title: The court of law governing the terms is in Romania
points.status: Terms of Use: "Country refers to: Romania". They further say how you must comply with the laws of "the Country", so this implies that they are based in Romania.

points.title: The service is only available in some countries approved by the United States government
points.status: Terms of Use: "You represent and warrant that (i) You are not located in a country that is subject to the United States government embargo, or that has been designated by the United States government as a "terrorist supporting" country, and (ii) You are not listed on any United States government list of prohibited or restricted parties"

points.title: Any liability on behalf of the service is only limited to the fees you paid as a user
points.status: Terms of Use: "Notwithstanding any damages that You might incur, the entire liability of the Company and any of its suppliers under any provision of this Terms and Your exclusive remedy for all of the foregoing shall be limited to the amount actually paid by You through the Service or 100 USD if You haven't purchased anything through the Service"
